function getCubeAttributes() {

    indices: new Uint16Array(CUBE_INDICES),
    positions: new Float32Array(CUBE_POSITIONS),
    normals: new Float32Array(CUBE_NORMALS),
    texCoords: new Float32Array(CUBE_TEX_COORDS)
  };
}
